| Name:  | LVA <<erstellen>> |
| Scope:  | Administration section of SAT |
| Level:  		  | User Goal     |
*-----------------+--------------+
| Actor:  | Admin |
| Interests:      | Administrator wants to create a new Lecture at the beginning of every Semester in order for students to register |
*-----------------+--------------+
| Preconditions:  | Logged in as Admin |
*-----------------+--------------+
| Main Scenario:  | 1. Admin creates a new lecture and must assign a name which does not have to be unique. |
|			 	  | 2. Admin may copy a Lecture from the previous Semester to save time, this data includes... |
|			      | 3. Admin may choose to set the Lecture active right away or at a later point (seperate Use Case) |
*-----------------+--------------+
| Special Requirements:	| Certain data should not be copied from an old Semester, particularly Student registrations  |
